gw.api.database

Class BundleSensitiveIterator<T extends KeyableBean>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.database.BundleSensitiveIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<T>

    public class BundleSensitiveIterator<T extends KeyableBean>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<T>
    Wraps an iterator (returned from a query) with a Predicate and ensures that all beans returned by the iterator still pass the Predicate after bundle refresh (i.e., the Predicate applied to the bean is true). It also ensures that beans that are returned are not retired, i.e., retired beans will be filtered out.
